          | you need; up to infinite boxes a year.
    .row
      .col
        //- svg
        //-   use
        img(
          height = "120"
          src = "/build/images/feature-linking.svg"
          width = "120"
        )
        h2.h2.header-thin Better Together
        p.p With Dixie cup and string technology, #{''}
          br
          | we are able to link boxes together.
      .col
        //- svg
        //-   use
        img(
          height = "120"
          src = "/build/images/feature-github.svg"
          width = "120"
        )
        h2.h2.header-thin Github Integrated
        p.p Run your branches, commits, #{''}
          br
          | and pull requests.
    .row
      a.btn.green More Features

  .hr
    span.hr-text or

